{"tid":827523,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超想贏！王嘉爾脫衣「麥克風都丟掉」 縱身一跳…金鐘國當場棄賽","createTime":"2018-09-19T03:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T04:29:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2841cb27a3856cca49c6a5721bcb3bbf146c1a2b","tid":827523,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"韓男團「GOT7」推出新專輯《Present: YOU》，近來除了宣傳，也短暫登上綜藝節目《Running Man》，跟主持群PK競賽。其中，王嘉爾（Jackson）在節目中燃燒勝負欲，為了取得更好的成績，甚至在鏡頭前直接把衣服、麥克風都脫掉，就只為了證明自己可以贏過金鐘國，開啟一場精采對決！<br />\n<br />\n節目中，GOT7和《RM》比賽「抓著腳拇指跳遠」，一開始所有成員都只有10公分左右，然而金鐘國一上場就輕鬆跳到32公分，刷新紀錄。王嘉爾不甘示弱，跳之前不斷深呼吸，最後居然一舉達到57公分，大贏金鐘國，讓強大的「老虎」也露出遺憾、受挫的表情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3564/d3564215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3564%2Fd3564215.jpg&h=d1d35b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲王嘉爾和金鐘國PK立定跳遠。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）<br />\n<br />\n見到這一幕，王嘉爾進一步要求加賽「直接立定跳」，並誇耀自己：「我真的可以跳很遠。」然後衝出來一跳，果然輕鬆就達到260公分左右，落地之後似乎非常滿意，還得意洋洋的回頭看金鐘國。金鐘國被激到，立刻重新上場，沒想到就這樣縱身一跳，落地位置明顯比王嘉爾還遠！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3564/d3564216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3564%2Fd3564216.jpg&h=5f5c5c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3564/d3564217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3564%2Fd3564217.jpg&h=93f65ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾為了贏，當場脫衣服和麥克風。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）<br />\n<br />\n比賽至此，《RM》成員都興奮大喊「贏了贏了」，沒想到反而徹底激發王嘉爾的勝負欲。他不顧一切，再度衝出來，還一口氣脫掉外衣，甚至說「麥克風不重要」，於是把別在身上的麥克風也扔掉，完全不管節目流程，就這樣硬是又跳了一次，一下子衝到將近3公尺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3564/d3564214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3564%2Fd3564214.jpg&h=1d795b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾得到金鐘國認證。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）<br />\n<br />\n面對這個結果，金鐘國看了一眼便認輸：「算你贏好了，Jackson贏了。」一秒放棄這個由王嘉爾挑起的比賽，消極態度反而害對方哭笑不得。不過，他最後也認證王嘉爾非常帥氣，並且跟《RM》成員一起送上掌聲，對於後輩努力的模樣，大方給予稱讚和肯定。<br />\n<br />\n上綜藝就是要過啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199ff1ce0a94c0e4f1b0e86120053b643ca88d8a","tid":827523,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"+2哥哥實在太skr了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775596001a594967f2ab10a542fd4235c49f28a8","tid":827523,"uid":169468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"矮仔"},{"pid":"af0449a2f59c1719f33ed317e21b7524821ec7ea","tid":827523,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"199ff1ce0a94c0e4f1b0e86120053b643ca88d8a","tid":827523,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"+2哥哥實在太skr了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QD4JiD5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQD4JiD5.gif&h=748cd3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦凡都讚好"},{"pid":"022a2174991947f4885b22876e3f6700f65b13a6","tid":827523,"uid":195806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"除衫真係可以跳遠d?"},{"pid":"9522e9cb66c1f6fb0864a5d44bd8b4dbbf1aa8ce","tid":827523,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"022a2174991947f4885b22876e3f6700f65b13a6","tid":827523,"uid":195806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:08:16.00